{"tid":1842143,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[大愛撚系列]病毒會挑選人性最脆弱的時候，乘虛而入！","createTime":"2020-01-25T14:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T22:33:35.000Z","uid":8557,"like":28,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"657936eb2849440de3bc1b2d7b0fdef15c765c20","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0kp507W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0kp507W.png&h=6af82ed9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtTq06W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtTq06W.png&h=055c5501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bQPtYTB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbQPtYTB.png&h=e20b1aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9SZ5yC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9SZ5yC.png&h=e5e38a48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n愛愛愛 愛乜鳩呀屌<br />\n用愛係咪可以拎黎消毒殺菌呀？<br />\n而家情況就係班強國閪物種自私到係全球播毒種菌,你就眾人皆醉我獨醒咁擺晒款宣揚你既大愛<br />\n真係睇撚到好扯火<br />\n大是大非只有二揀一嘅情況下,到今天都仲有呢種人企係道德高地講啲山係石頭海係水既廢話,做乜撚野啫你<br />\n咁有愛返上去武漢到宣揚啦<br />\n大愛呀？等我幫你宣揚下你既理念等多啲人念力抗武漢肺炎啦"},{"pid":"e194aca6743776a5645438d6fa9b09635f1d99c2","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:06:51.000Z","msg":"on9婆"},{"pid":"2ed38f269a200b1e5f764edefb6077a3f0ed4ce5","tid":1842143,"uid":218855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4b1bdfdc8517d9fa93e390a66c8dc774948862","tid":1842143,"uid":259532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"弱智左膠上撚晒腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"424b1add21f875defbdc5b489c575b50853a583a","tid":1842143,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"關我咩事 大把呢啲人 逐個post 上嚟咪好唔得閒"},{"pid":"9b29ff4fcdfc5714c05834ded1de0578db5dc606","tid":1842143,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"-O-O 讓他來吧"},{"pid":"e4fc001af96e4659d8a7216bd1303dad7e15af5d","tid":1842143,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:31:19.000Z","msg":"-0-0"},{"pid":"0ccaafcc683a671e006d2363b5a950af2527b6ae","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"424b1add21f875defbdc5b489c575b50853a583a","tid":1842143,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:30:11.000Z","msg":"關我咩事 大把呢啲人 逐個post 上嚟咪好唔得閒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:37:16.000Z","msg":"咁你咪出返去囉 唔關你事又要入黎又要睇又要回"},{"pid":"a57ef9392352dcfe70b12bc23dfb07ecac143575","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e4b1bdfdc8517d9fa93e390a66c8dc774948862","tid":1842143,"uid":259532,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"弱智左膠上撚晒腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T17:46:36.000Z","msg":"好撚on9呀真係<br />\n對疾病有正確認知 配合防疫政策<br />\n屌你中學做project咩屌,列撚晒main point出黎就好似好有理據咁<br />\n又唔撚知離撚晒地,講嗰兩樣野一樣就專家都仲搵緊呀臭閪,另一樣就連個閪政府都唔撚做呀,點撚樣配合呀你老母,交配你老母就得臭閪<br />\n真係乜撚都唔撚識架喎屌"},{"pid":"371e571e492c5c85ebfb9288eb6a25ef5f9bd520","tid":1842143,"uid":241173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T04:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9b7d2520a05a3d0c25651db9030762907de188","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T06:07:16.000Z","msg":"<img 