like":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51b82193799aa87f4c192bb1ff5d396ccbf184c6","tid":1842143,"uid":240665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"扮曬大愛想拎光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就唔信佢心底係咁諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T11:40:28.000Z","msg":"直情虛偽到仆街啦<br />\n講埋D模稜兩可既野又唔撚使成本<br />\n仲可以話俾人聽自己係一個天使心腸好好<br />\n喂!屌你老母!唔撚識就出少句野啦!"},{"pid":"f3f1797d42cbb3b7bac4da0ea204c389807e6b98","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aqq1Nz2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faqq1Nz2.jpg&h=57130c99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等澳門大大力一巴打落你個臭閪塊面到"},{"pid":"1aee21b37242b9c170a6772d44d8393d68cf7b6b","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"非本地居民確診可以唔使錢黎睇醫生啦<br />\n係唔撚係要配合防疫政策呀又<br />\n你老味！真係好撚嬲！"},{"pid":"f3a71c30bd6d7e0f033e0f2f46aed9198cea5e4d","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T13:23:40.000Z","msg":"喂 封關啦<br />\n收鳩非香港人錢啦<br />\n港共閪政府歧視你愛既子民啦candy tse"},{"pid":"1ef87cdb47b6085a0f7e07e39327d9364551b965","tid":1842143,"uid":344033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n手足裝備抗沙士：防毒面具/濾罐 (型號/分析/用法/清潔全齊）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1848447\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1848447</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整體分析圖：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F116690396531818%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=bcd9fd91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/116690396531818/?d=n</a><br />\n個別仔細分析：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">護目鏡</span>：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845419\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845419</a></span></span> / <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F112357283631796%2Fposts%2F117867026414155%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=86415723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/112357283631796/posts/117867026414155/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\nVPN 大踢爆：<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D112386483628876%26id%3D112357283631796%26__tn__%3D%252As-R&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=7ea6e69c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=112386483628876&amp;id=112357283631796&amp;__tn__=%2As-R</a><br />\n<br />\n請大家廣傳，避免沉底<br />\n<br />\n最近口罩同N95 都賣曬，部分手足屋企口罩已經就黎用盡，今日同大家介紹下可以防沙士+TG嘅濾罐同濾棉。第一，係for 用曬/買唔到口罩嘅手足，第二係希望方便大家一次過買齊發夢+出街嘅裝備，就算沙士完左，自用送禮都可以繼續名貴大方。<br />\n<br />\nN95/R95/P95 口罩基本上係particulate respirator, 外科口罩防嘅係飛沫粒子，即係我地用防毒面具代替，就要裝particulate filter，換言之，就係濾棉！<br />\n<br />\n濾棉最高級別就係P100，防油性+非油性粒子，即係TG（油性）同埋病毒都可以防，型號包括2091, 2097, 2297, 6035（只有英國製）,7093 等等，而60926等等嘅6092X 系列濾罐，因為內置P100 濾棉，所以一樣ok <br />\n其中，6053 同 7093 棉係防水的，清潔消毒會較方便，而60926表面亦有膠盒。<br />\n<br />\n有強國人做過測試，係北京霧霾毒氣之下，3M 2091 用左十一日過濾能力都係跌左1%，手足請自行考慮幾耐換一次。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon 大log買亦有便，大家可以組團買。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com.au%2F3M%2Fen_AU%2Fcompany-au%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B8711017%2B3294471754%26rt%3Drud&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=233d207f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com.au/3M/en_AU/company-au/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-6035-P2-P3/?N=5002385+8711017+3294471754&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.3m.com%2F3M%2Fen_US%2Fcompany-us%2Fall-3m-products%2F~%2F3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case%2F%3FN%3D5002385%2B3294776429%26rt%3Drud&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=3c0ab8f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.3m.com/3M/en_US/company-us/all-3m-products/~/3M-Particulate-Filter-7093-P100-60-EA-Case/?N=5002385+3294776429&amp;rt=rud</a><br />\n<br />\n2003 年沙士，淘大嘅清理人員就係用2091棉+600X 罐（罐理論上唔洗，應該係防佢地嘅清潔同消毒藥水）。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">如何清潔防毒面具可參考依段片，有教disinfection，主要都係漂白水同消毒劑<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdE5IweYn3T4&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=bed71e39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dE5IweYn3T4</a></span></span><br />\n<br />\n清潔步驟：<br />\n入到屋企唔好除裝備住，用酒精紙巾抹左面具同濾棉/罐表面先，跟住抹埋手再洗手（點解又要酒精又要洗手係有原因的），跟住就除面罩，再跟番片入面嘅教學清潔<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n防毒面具方面，建議大家買/用6800 或者其他包曬成塊面嘅款式，咁樣就唔洗帶眼罩，一舊野保護曬成塊面，最安全。因為你戴半面+眼罩，咁就多舊野清潔，同埋部分眼罩封唔曬，冇咁安全。<br />\n<br />\n型號方面，全面嘅建議大家買6800，順便擋埋橡膠子彈，半面嘅就買7502/ 6500，兩款手足都表示舒適度幾高。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112044766987392%2Fposts%2F119490526242816%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=fb4fe49a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112044766987392/posts/119490526242816/?d=n</a><br />\n酒精搓手液 vs 洗手梘液</span>"},{"pid":"478cb78ea4d4b74460420ba769b276853bc31827","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T07:40:07.000Z","msg":"binc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb4e99f1ef6b34e4074a049fa2bc233fcc6d4ecc","tid":1842143,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"你真係好撚好彩呀candy tse<br />\n你自己睇下個傻閪偽善肉鳩酸既范瑋琪落得咩下場<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f06b33bb527d520fe67dad20e674955c8f1039b","tid":1842143,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T18:32:39.000Z","msg":"[狼人] 武漢肺炎大逃殺<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRUVAYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRUVAYN.jpg&h=68e67bab&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}